  <li>
    <h3><a href="http://www.wamibrew.com">Wamibrew</a></h3>
    <p>Wamibrew (<em>W</em>hat <em>Am</em> <em>I</em> <em>Brew</em>ing?) is a Rails-based algorithmic beer recipe generator for homebrewers.
      It semi-randomly assembles a brewable recipe (based on some general rules and probabilities)
      and then attempts to heuristically determine the closest recognized style of the generated recipe.  Every recipe guaranteed to make booze!
    </p>
